column2:
We have invested a lot of time and effort in
creating COVID-19 Data Hub, please cite the
following when using it:

  Guidotti, E., Ardia, D., (2020), "COVID-19 Data
  Hub", Journal of Open Source Software
  5(51):2376, doi: 10.21105/joss.02376

The implementation details and the latest version
of the data are described in:

  Guidotti, E., (2022), "A worldwide
  epidemiological database for COVID-19 at
  fine-grained spatial resolution", Sci Data
  9(1):112, doi: 10.1038/s41597-022-01245-1
To print citations in BibTeX format use:
To hide this message use 'verbose = FALSE'.
